    "custom_liquid_bYHGCJ": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "Custom Liquid",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>\n/* ===== Page Layout ===== */\n.page-container {\n  max-width: 1100px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  padding: 20px;\n  font-family: inherit;\n}\n\n/* ===== Section Styling ===== */\n.section-bone {\n  margin-bottom: 48px;\n}\n\n.section-bone h2 {\n  margin-bottom: 14px;\n  font-size: 26px;\n}\n\n.section-bone h3 {\n  margin-top: 22px;\n  margin-bottom: 10px;\n  font-size: 20px;\n}\n\n.section-bone p {\n  margin-bottom: 12px;\n  line-height: 1.7;\n  color: #374151;\n}\n\n.section-bone ul,\n.section-bone ol {\n  margin: 14px 0 18px;\n  padding-left: 20px;\n}\n\n.section-bone li {\n  margin-bottom: 8px;\n}\n\n/* ===== Blockquote ===== */\n.blockquote {\n  margin-top: 18px;\n  padding: 14px 16px;\n  background: #f1f5f9;\n  border-left: 4px solid #4f6fae;\n  color: #334155;\n}\n\n/* ===== Comparison Table ===== */\n.comparison-table {\n  width: 100%;\n  border-collapse: separate;\n  border-spacing: 0;\n  margin-top: 20px;\n  background: #ffffff;\n  border-radius: 10px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);\n}\n\n.comparison-table th {\n  background: #4f6fae;\n  color: #ffffff;\n  padding: 14px 12px;\n  font-size: 15px;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n\n.comparison-table td {\n  padding: 14px 12px;\n  font-size: 14px;\n  text-align: center;\n  border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\n}\n\n.comparison-table td:first-child {\n  text-align: left;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  background: #f9fafb;\n}\n\n.comparison-table tr:nth-child(even) td {\n  background: #f8fafc;\n}\n\n/* ===== FAQ ===== */\n.faq-item {\n  margin-bottom: 22px;\n  padding-bottom: 18px;\n  border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;\n}\n\n.faq-question {\n  font-size: 17px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  margin-bottom: 8px;\n  line-height: 1.4;\n}\n\n.faq-answer {\n  font-size: 15px;\n  line-height: 1.7;\n  color: #374151;\n}\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"page-container\">\n\n  <!-- Intro -->\n  <section class=\"section-bone\">\n    <h2>What Are Bone Conduction Headphones & Earphones?</h2>\n    <p><strong>Bone conduction headphones or bone conduction earphones</strong> transmit sound through your cheekbones, bypassing the eardrum entirely.</p>\n    <p>This allows you to hear music while staying aware of your surroundings — ideal for runners, cyclists, and people with hearing concerns.</p>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- How it works -->\n  <section class=\"section-bone\">\n    <h2>How Do Bone Conduction Headphones Work?</h2>\n    <p>They use transducers that send vibrations through your bones directly to the cochlea (inner ear), bypassing the eardrum.</p>\n    <p>This keeps your ear canal open for ambient awareness.</p>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- Comparison -->\n  <section class=\"section-bone\">\n    <h2>Bone Conduction vs Traditional Headphones</h2>\n\n    <table class=\"comparison-table\">\n      <tr>\n        <th>Feature</th>\n        <th>Bone Conduction</th>\n        <th>Regular Headphones</th>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Safety</td>\n        <td>Lets outside sound in</td>\n        <td>Blocks noise</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Comfort</td>\n        <td>No ear pressure</td>\n        <td>Can cause fatigue</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Sound Quality</td>\n        <td>Mids / Highs focused</td>\n        <td>Full bass & clarity</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Best For</td>\n        <td>Sports, awareness</td>\n        <td>Music immersion</td>\n      </tr>\n    </table>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- FAQ -->\n  <section class=\"section-bone\">\n    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"faq-question\"><strong>1. Are Bone Conduction Headphones or Earphones Safe?</strong></h3>\n      <p class=\"faq-answer\">Yes. Bone conduction headphones are FDA-approved and safer for long-term use as they bypass the eardrum.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"faq-question\"><strong>2. Are bone conduction headphones bad for you?</strong></h3>\n      <p class=\"faq-answer\">No, they are safe when used responsibly at moderate volume levels.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"faq-question\"><strong>3. Are bone conduction headphones better for your hearing?</strong></h3>\n      <p class=\"faq-answer\">Yes, they reduce strain on the eardrum and are a safer alternative for long listening sessions.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"faq-question\"><strong>4. Can bone conduction headphones cause hearing loss?</strong></h3>\n      <p class=\"faq-answer\">No, unless used at extremely high volumes for extended periods.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"faq-question\"><strong>5. Can bone conduction headphones help with hearing loss?</strong></h3>\n      <p class=\"faq-answer\">They can help people with conductive hearing loss, but they do not restore hearing completely.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"faq-question\"><strong>6. Can bone conduction headphones cause headaches?</strong></h3>\n      <p class=\"faq-answer\">Rarely. Improper fit or high volume may cause discomfort, which can be avoided with correct usage.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"faq-question\"><strong>7. When should you use bone conduction headphones?</strong></h3>\n      <p class=\"faq-answer\">They are ideal for workouts, commuting, office work, and situations requiring awareness.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"faq-question\"><strong>8. Are bone conduction headphones waterproof?</strong></h3>\n      <p class=\"faq-answer\">Some models are waterproof or water-resistant. Always check the IP rating.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"faq-question\"><strong>9. Can bone conduction headphones be used for swimming?</strong></h3>\n      <p class=\"faq-answer\">Yes, IP68-rated models are designed specifically for swimming.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <h3 class=\"faq-question\"><strong>10. Can bone conduction headphones be used for phone calls?</strong></h3>\n      <p class=\"faq-answer\">Yes, most models include built-in microphones for hands-free calling.</p>\n    </div>\n\n  </section>\n\n</div>",
